  m_Name: Quinns
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalSO
  title: Sweet Salvation
  entry: Oh how irradiant you are. Your sweet porcelain body which is nullified from
    this numbing rot down here. In all piles of bones I've tread through you are
    my anchor- My guiding light. I'll seek you- Embrace me- Save me.
  number: 2
